Package: skater
Title: Utilities for SNP-Based Kinship Analysis
Description: Utilities for SNP-based kinship analysis testing and evaluation.  
    The skater package contains functions for importing, parsing, and analyzing 
    pedigree data, performing relationship degree inference, benchmarking relationship 
    degree classification, and summarizing identity by descent (IBD) segment data.
Version: 0.1.0
